        <strong class="text-white">Generative engine optimisation is an eight-step programme</strong> that moves your brand from absent in AI-generated answers to consistently cited across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Gemini, Copilot, and Google AI Overviews. This guide gives you every step in order, with the rationale, practical actions, and common mistakes for each.
