        <span class="eyebrow">Key Takeaways</span>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-200">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-[var(--accent)]">&#10003;</span>
            <span>The AI visibility audit is the non-negotiable first step — every subsequent decision depends on the baseline it establishes.</span>
