            <span>Citation architecture — definitional openings, short paragraphs, FAQ sections, schema markup — is the highest-leverage content practice.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-[var(--accent)]">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Each AI platform has different citation logic. A strategy targeting only one platform will miss the majority of AI search traffic.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-[var(--accent)]">&#10003;</span>
            <span>GEO is a programme, not a project. Weekly monitoring and monthly iteration are what turn one-off gains into compounding citation share.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
